			"offsets": {
				"from": 0,
				"to": 3700
			},
			"text": " Hey, this is Brian from Fullstack Egg."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:03,700",
				"to": "00:00:05,900"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 3700,
				"to": 5900
			},
			"text": " Before we set up paperless,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:05,900",
				"to": "00:00:09,100"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 5900,
				"to": 9100
			},
			"text": " we're going to need somewhere to install it."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:09,100",
				"to": "00:00:13,980"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 9100,
				"to": 13980
			},
			"text": " We could install it on our own computer at home."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:13,980",
				"to": "00:00:16,540"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 13980,
				"to": 16540
			},
			"text": " Or if we want to install it in the Cloud,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:16,540",
				"to": "00:00:19,220"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 16540,
				"to": 19220
			},
			"text": " we could set up a VPS."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:19,220",
				"to": "00:00:23,140"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 19220,
				"to": 23140
			},
			"text": " VPS stands for Virtual Private Server."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:23,140",
				"to": "00:00:25,460"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 23140,
				"to": 25460
			},
			"text": " You can think of it as renting"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:25,460",
				"to": "00:00:29,980"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 25460,
				"to": 29980
			},
			"text": " a small office space instead of buying your own building."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:29,980",
				"to": "00:00:34,780"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 29980,
				"to": 34780
			},
			"text": " Someone else owns the building and handles all the maintenance,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:34,780",
				"to": "00:00:37,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 34780,
				"to": 37940
			},
			"text": " and you just use the space."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:37,940",
				"to": "00:00:42,620"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 37940,
				"to": 42620
			},
			"text": " Setting up a VPS is just like renting an office."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:42,620",
				"to": "00:00:47,980"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 42620,
				"to": 47980
			},
			"text": " A company like DigitalOcean has huge data centers full of servers."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:47,980",
				"to": "00:00:51,300"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 47980,
				"to": 51300
			},
			"text": " You rent just a slice of one of those servers."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:51,300",
				"to": "00:00:52,660"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 51300,
				"to": 52660
			},
			"text": " It's always on,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:52,660",
				"to": "00:00:54,820"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 52660,
				"to": 54820
			},
			"text": " always connected to the Internet,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:54,820",
				"to": "00:00:58,340"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 54820,
				"to": 58340
			},
			"text": " and you can run whatever you want to install on it."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:58,340",
				"to": "00:01:02,260"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 58340,
				"to": 62260
			},
			"text": " Here's what setting up a VPS actually looks like."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:02,260",
				"to": "00:01:05,660"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 62260,
				"to": 65660
			},
			"text": " On DigitalOcean, they call a VPS a droplet."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:05,660",
				"to": "00:01:10,540"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 65660,
				"to": 70540
			},
			"text": " You pick the size you need based on your software requirements."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:10,540",
				"to": "00:01:15,300"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 70540,
				"to": 75300
			},
			"text": " For paperless, we're going to need something with about four gigs of memory."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:15,300",
				"to": "00:01:19,740"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 75300,
				"to": 79740
			},
			"text": " On DigitalOcean, that's going to run us about 24 bucks a month,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:19,740",
				"to": "00:01:23,100"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 79740,
				"to": 83100
			},
			"text": " which is less than a lot of software subscriptions,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:23,100",
				"to": "00:01:25,860"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 83100,
				"to": 85860
			},
			"text": " and you own everything on it."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:25,860",
				"to": "00:01:27,860"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 85860,
				"to": 87860
			},
			"text": " As you can see here,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:27,860",
				"to": "00:01:30,660"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 87860,
				"to": 90660
			},
			"text": " you can choose the region your server lives in,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:30,660",
				"to": "00:01:34,900"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 90660,
				"to": 94900
			},
			"text": " so you're going to want to just choose whatever is closest to you."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:34,900",
				"to": "00:01:37,980"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 94900,
				"to": 97980
			},
			"text": " I'm sure when you hear $24 a month,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:37,980",
				"to": "00:01:41,900"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 97980,
				"to": 101900
			},
			"text": " you're thinking, \"Why not just run this on my own computer?\""
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:41,900",
				"to": "00:01:45,860"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 101900,
				"to": 105860
			},
			"text": " You totally can do that, but a VPS is always on,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:45,860",
				"to": "00:01:50,340"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 105860,
				"to": 110340
			},
			"text": " even when your home Internet goes down or you turn off your laptop,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:50,340",
				"to": "00:01:53,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 110340,
				"to": 113940
			},
			"text": " and when you want to access your documents from your phone in the field,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:53,940",
				"to": "00:01:57,980"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 113940,
				"to": 117980
			},
			"text": " the VPS is already on the Internet and ready to go."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:57,980",
				"to": "00:02:02,140"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 117980,
				"to": 122140
			},
			"text": " So that's it. A VPS is just a computer you write online."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:02,140",
				"to": "00:02:05,740"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 122140,
				"to": 125740
			},
			"text": " In a later video, we'll walk you through actually creating one of these"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:05,740",
				"to": "00:02:08,940"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 125740,
